{"tid":1083950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉燕卿：若涉公眾利益　政府無理由拒公開資料","createTime":"2019-03-30T04:40:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T04:40:35.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ca0cf0f2ac3f09eb7575e2b951ca70ef948b276b","tid":1083950,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T04:40:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190330/s00001/fde189730b729cf7dfd991ba4d7ab789.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190330%2Fs00001%2Ffde189730b729cf7dfd991ba4d7ab789.jpg&h=748fec66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n申訴專員劉燕卿下周一卸任，她今早在港台節目《香港家書》表示，申訴專員公署收到有關公開資料的投訴數字一直高踞不下；政府部門有各種理由拒絕公開資料，例如部門沒有備存相關數據、編製資料會耗用大量資源，或受制於與第三方所訂立的協議條款等。<br />\n<br />\n劉燕卿提出，若市民索取的資料涉及重大公眾利益或屬廣受關注的課題，「部門沒有理由繼續拒絕備存相關統計數據，或不願安排額外人手編製資料」。<br />\n<br />\n她又稱，如果若干協議條款有窒礙開明問責之嫌，導致政府無法開誠布公，政府日後訂立的協議便應剔除這類條款，除非有真正需要保障敏感資料。"},{"pid":"5f833df05386f733b7a9a71e513eac77c21ec95a","tid":1083950,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T04:40:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190330/s00001/1553915669321/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190330%2Fs00001%2F1553915669321%2F&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7R9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=b13c0fdf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190330%2Fs00001%2F1553915669321%2F&h=a081a04b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190330/s00001/1553915669321/</a>"}]}